Package: WorldMapR
Type: Package
Title: Worldwide or Continent-Based Heat Maps
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Luigi", "Annicchiarico", email = "luigi.annic@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut"))
    )
Description: Easily plot heat maps of the whole world
    or subsections, based on continuous or categorical data. You can also add country labels to the map. 
